eter%20Todd%2C%20the%20supposed%20creator%20of%20bitcoin%20according%20to%20a%20new%20documentary%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros%20Discovery%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20HBO%20documentary%20says%20that%20Canadian%20programmer%20Peter%20Todd%20is%20the%20creator%20of%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20points%20to%20several%20things%20to%20back%20the%20claim%2C%20but%20Todd%20denies%20he%20is%20the%20token's%20creator.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20true%20identity%20of%20Satoshi%20Nakamoto%2C%20who%20wrote%20the%20bitcoin%20white%20paper%2C%20has%20been%20hotly%20debated.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20HBO%20documentary%20suggests%20the%20identity%20of%20bitcoin's%20inventor%20is%20a%20Canadian%20programmer%20named%20Peter%20Todd.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20Electric%3A%20The%20Bitcoin%20Mystery%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20premiered%20on%20HBO%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20names%20Todd%20as%20bitcoin's%20pseudonymous%20creator%2C%20Satoshi%20Nakamoto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crypto%20community%20had%20been%20anticipating%20a%20potential%20reveal%20in%20the%20documentary%2C%20though%20Todd%20was%20not%20among%20the%20most%20commonly%20cited%20names%20people%20had%20been%20expecting.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto%20watchers%20were%20focused%20on%20figures%20including%20programmer%20Len%20Sassaman%2C%20computer%20scientist%20Nick%20Szabo%2C%20and%20Blockstream%20CEO%20Adam%20Back.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fmeme-coins-bitcoin-inventor-surge-len-sassaman-crypto-hbo-documentary-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20slew%20of%20meme%20coins%20named%20after%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20debuted%20ahead%20of%20the%20documentary%20and%20saw%20huge%20swings%20as%20traders%20placed%20bets%20on%20who%20the%20documentary%20would%20name.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETodd%2C%20an%20applied%20cryptography%20consultant%20at%20GitHub%2C%20has%20been%20mostly%20overlooked%20but%20filmmaker%20Cullen%20Hoback%20s