%3D%5C%22The%20oceanview%20family%20room%20on%20the%20NCL%20Breakaway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6c25675c877a99b6132c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223838%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECurtains%20could%20cover%20the%20window%20port.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20cabin%20measured%20218%20square%20feet%2C%20according%20to%20Norwegian.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20only%20three%20people%2C%20we%20didn't%20feel%20like%20we%20were%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other%20and%20had%20enough%20foot%20space%20to%20easily%20navigate%20around%20luggage%2C%20beds%2C%20and%20other%20clutter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room%20boasted%20a%20grey%2C%20white%2C%20and%20purple%20color%20palette%2C%20which%20we%20found%20boring%20but%20not%20a%20total%20eyesore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20decor%20was%20basic%20compared%20to%20newer%20ships.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Norwegian%20Prima%20oceanview%20stateroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c84f3617692f0d03e65cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20oceanview%20stateroom%20on%20Norwegian%20Prima.%3Cp%3ENorwegian%20Cruise%20Line%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENorwegian's%20newer%20ships%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorwegian-cruise-ships-breakaway-prima-compared-review-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrima%2C%20feature%20elegant%20staterooms%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20resemble%20a%20contemporary%20boutique%20hotel%20with%20more%20modern%20lighting%2C%20colors%2C%20and%20artwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20curtain%20separated%20the%202%20sleeping%20areas.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20husband%20on%20the%20main%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67056f0f198738e3a70f1ea1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20husband%20posing%20for%20scale.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20chose%20this%20specific%20cabin%20type%20because%20of%20the%20curtain%20that%20separates%20the%20room.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20slept%20on%20the%20main%20bed%20while%20my%20mom%20took%20the%20sofa%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20curtain%20provided%20privacy%20for%20changing%20and%20sleeping.%20This%20was%20a%20perfect%20setup%20since%20we%20all%20three%20already%20live%20together%20in%20our%20normal%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20oceanview%20rooms%20on%20Breakaway%20don't%20have%20the%20curtain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sofa%20bed%20was%20more%20of%20an%20oversized%20twin.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Breakaway%20sofa%20converted%20into%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67056f3e198738e3a70f1eda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221612%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sofa%20bed%20wasn't%20quite%20the%20size%20of%20a%20regular%20double.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENorwegian%20markets%20its%20sofa%20bed%20as%20a%20double%2C%20but%20it's%20really%20only%20comfortable%20enough%20for%20one%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20would%20likely%20be%20big%20enough%20to%20accommodate%20two%20kids%20or%20younger%20teenagers.%20However%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20two%20adults%20as%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20couldn't%20fit%20comfortably%20when%20we%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sofa%20bed%20is%20hard%2C%20while%20the%20main%20bed%20is%20soft.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20main%20bed%20is%20white%20with%20beige%20walls.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67056f6ea703186492804eb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20main%20bed%20could%20be%20split%20into%20two%20twins%20or%20combined%20into%20a%20queen.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20noticed%20the%20main%20bed%20was%20very%20plush%20and%20soft.%20However%2C%20the%20sofa%20bed%20had%20a%20harder%20surface.%20My%20mom%20didn't%20mind%20but%20said%20it%20started%20getting%20old%20after%20night%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20my%20husband%20switched%20beds%20some%20nights%20to%20give%20her%20the%20soft%20one%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0problem%20solved!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pullman%20bed%20looked%20miserable.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pullman%20popped%20out%20of%20the%20ceiling%20above%20the%20sofa%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67056fe13f2165d716df4fd7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20didn't%20need%20the%20pullman%2C%20thankfully.%20%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth%20sleeping%20spot%20in%20the%20oceanview%20family%20cabin%20is%20one%20that%20pulls%20down%20from%20the%20ceiling%20above%20the%20sofa%20pullout%20%E2%80%94%20basically%20creating%20a%20bunk%20bed.%20A%20ladder%20is%20provided%20to%20get%20up%20and%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20I%20can%20see%20it%20working%20for%20kids.%20Older%20teenagers%20and%20young%20adults%2C%20however%2C%20would%20likely%20find%20the%20space%20way%20too%20cramped%20for%20comfort%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sleeping%20on%20that%20top%20bunk%20would%20be%20my%20personal%20nightmare.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20the%20risk%20of%20falling%20off%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20some%20people%20would%20feel%20claustrophobic.%20It's%20also%20why%20my%20family%20didn't%20consider%20staying%20in%20the%20cheapest%20four-person%20inside%20the%20cabin%20%E2%80%94%20none%20of%20us%20wanted%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20pullman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20a%20swivel%20television%20and%20a%20vanity.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20television%20and%20vanity.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67057014a703186492804f00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20impossible%20to%20avoid%20having%20clutter%20around%20the%20space.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20television%20could%20swivel%20between%20to%20face%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20curtain%20but%20was%20on%20the%20side%20closest%20to%20the%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vanity%20was%20also%20on%20the%20window%2C%20giving%20my%20mom%20plenty%20of%20space%20to%20do%20her%20makeup%20while%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20used%20the%20bathroom%20mirror%20to%20get%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOutlets%20and%20charging%20ports%20were%20minimal.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20charging%20ports.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670570323f2165d716df503a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221393%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20outlets%20were%20restricted%20to%20the%20vanity.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlets%20were%20on%20the%20vanity%2C%20and%20there%20were%20only%20a%20few%20spots%20to%20plug%20in.%20It%20was%20pretty%20inconvenient%20since%20we%20had%20to%20take%20turns%20charging%20all%20of%20our%20separate%20items%2C%20like%20phones%2C%20tablets%2C%20watches%2C%20and%20portable%20chargers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20bring%20a%20cruise-approved%20power%20strip%20for%20more%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20were%202%20closets%20and%20plenty%20of%20shelves.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20storage%20options%2C%20including%20the%20brown%20closets%20and%20shelves.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67057146a703186492804f78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20storage%20space%20available%2C%20including%20the%20extra%20closet%20(top%20left).%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom's%20side%20of%20the%20room%20had%20its%20own%20closet%2C%20albeit%20smaller%20than%20the%20one%20by%20the%20main%20bed.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20more%20than%20enough%20space%20for%20all%20of%20our%20hanging%20clothes%20and%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20shelves%20throughout%20the%20cabin%2C%20as%20well%20as%20cabinets%20under%20the%20vanity%20for%20extra%20storage.%20To%20optimize%20space%2C%20we%20unpacked%20and%20put%20our%20suitcases%20under%20the%20main%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGuests%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20safe%20and%20refrigerator.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20black%20refrigerator%20under%20the%20vanity.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6705715f3f2165d716df50a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20refrigerator%20under%20the%20vanity.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20liked%20the%20refrigerator%20for%20keeping%20water%20cold%20but%20didn't%20take%20any%20of%20the%20stocked%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safe%20is%20in%20the%20main%20closet%20and%20is%20perfect%20for%20things%20like%20cash%2C%20passports%2C%20and%20other%20valuables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bathroom%20was%20huge%20for%20a%20cruise%20ship.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20giant%20bathroom%20with%20beige%20walls%20and%20shower%2Ftub%20combo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6705718da703186492804f8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20had%20enough%20tabletop%20space%20and%20hooks%20to%20hang%20towels.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20cruise%20cabins%20can%20have%20a%20painfully%20small%20bathroom%2C%20but%20Breakaway's%20family%20oceanview%20boasted%20dual%20sinks%20and%20a%20shower%2Ftub%20combo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20proved%20to%20be%20more%20than%20enough%20space.%20The%20shower%20came%20with%20shampoo%20and%20body%20wash%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGuests%20can%20opt%20out%20of%20housekeeping.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20brown%20stateroom%20door.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670571de3f2165d716df50eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20light%20above%20the%20door%20is%20a%20signal%20for%20housekeeping.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20switch%20in%20the%20cabin's%20entryway%20could%20indicate%20to%20staff%20whether%20we%20wanted%20housekeeping%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20only%20opted%20for%20this%20on%20one%20day%2C%20but%20it%20was%20nice%20not%20having%20to%20track%20down%20an%20employee%20to%20ask%20them%20not%20to%20make%20up%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20think%20the%20oceanview%20family%20cabin%20is%20perfect%20for%203%20adults.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221786%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20space%20with%20the%20sofa%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67057210a703186492804fe1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221339%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20separate%20sleeping%20area%20with%20the%20sofa%20bed%20was%20the%20selling%20point%20for%20my%20family.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20minimal%20chargin