0such%20as%20the%20%243%20billion%20hedge-fund%20platform%20Crestline%20Summit%2C%20it%20is%20a%20part%20of%20their%20expansion%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Texas-based%20manager%20launched%20its%20multi-strategy%20offering%20in%202015%20out%20of%20the%20firm's%20existing%20fund-of-funds%20business.%20In%20May%2C%20it%20launched%20a%20leveraged%20version%20of%20its%20flagship%20stable%20value%20strategy%2C%20offering%20investors%20in%20its%20three%20strategies%20a%20cash%20hurdle%20for%20performance%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20still%20charges%20management%20fees%20to%20cover%20operating%20expenses%20and%20pass-through%20fees%20to%20pay%20its%2030%20portfolio%20managers.%20The%20cash%20hurdle%2C%20which%20means%20they%20only%20get%20paid%20for%20performance%20above%20Treasury%20bills%2C%20also%20comes%20with%20more%20of%20a%20payout%20for%20the%20firm%20if%20the%20manager%20significantly%20outperforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20alignment%20with%20forward-thinking%20LPs%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20put%20the%20portfolio%20managers%20or%20the%20fund%20managers%20in%20such%20a%20position%20that%20they%20don't%20make%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Caroline%20Cooley%2C%20Crestline%20Summit's%20chief%20investment%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20give-and-take%20where%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20charge%20on%20the%20interest-rate%20component%20of%20the%20return%2C%20but%20we%20will%20charge%20a%20higher%20rate%20for%20the%20alpha%20component%20of%20the%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECash%20hurdles%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20more%20common%20thanks%20to%20higher%20interest%20rates%20and%20vocal%20allocators%20such%20as%20the%20Teacher%20Retirement%20System%20of%20Texas%2C%20which%20led%20a%20group%20of%20dozens%20of%20investors%20to%20call%20for%20such%20fee%20agreements%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pionline.com%2Fhedge-funds%2Fpension-funds-consultants-press-cash-hurdles-hedge-fund-fee-arrangements%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20open%20letter%20earlier%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20ExodusPoint%2C%20the%20New%20York-based%20fund%20run%20by%20Michael%20Gelband%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexoduspoint-multistrategy-hedge-funds-lower-fees-adopt-cash-hurdle-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20the%20most%20prominent%20hedge%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20adopt%20such%20a%20structure%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20hurdles%20are%20just%20one%20element%20of%20Crestline's%20overall%20plans.%20This%20business%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20%2418%20billion%20alternatives%20manager%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bin%20expansion%20mode%2C%20full%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Neilson%20Arbour%2C%20the%20deputy%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Crestline%20Summit.%20The%20manager%20plans%20to%20add%20up%20to%20four%20more%20PMs%20this%20year.%20While%20the%20battle%20for%20talent%20among%20multimanagers%20is%20not%20cheap%2C%20the%20firm%20hopes%20its%20flexibility%20will%20win%20over%20PMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20at%20this%20inflection%20point%2C%20this%20escape%20velocity%2C%20of%20where%20the%20business%20is%20and%20where%20we%20see%20it%20growing%20to%2C%20and%20we're%20excited%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Arbour%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1d782b4-ebc0-4406-adb9-2127aa6e366a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20than%20just%20compensation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20bet-on-themselves%20fee%20structure%2C%20the%20firm%20believes%20it%20can%20attract%20capital%2C%20and%20its%20newest%20offering%20includes%20backing%20from%20the%20massive%20pension%20fund%20Texas%20Teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20culture%20is%20why%20leaders%20believe%20talent%20will%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20pay%20competitive%20rates%20for%20people.%20But%20we%20also%20recognize%20that%20in%20a%20world%20where%20everyone%20has%20a%20job%2C%20people%20take%20jobs%20for%20lots%20of%20different%20reasons%2C%20of%20which%20pay%20is%20one%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Arbour%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bcapital%20and%20economics%20are%20commoditized%20to%20a%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrestline%20believes%20it%20is%20more%20flexible%20with%20PMs%20than%20larger%20pod%20peers.%20Roughly%20half%20of%20its%20PMs%20operate%20externally%2C%20meaning%20they're%20able%20to%20raise%20additional%20capital%20alongside%20Crestline's%20investment.%20One%20such%20manager%20is%20former%20Citadel%20PM%20Josh%20White%2C%20who%20started%20trading%20at%20his%20London-based%20Regents%20Gate%20earlier%20this%20year%20with%20capital%20from%20Crestline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20might%20enable%20you%20to%20find%20the%20person%20that's%20been%20kind%20of%20a%20cog%20in%20the%20wheel%20of%20a%20platform%20for%20all%20of%20their%20life%2C%20and%20now%20they%20want%20their%20name%20on%20the%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooley%20said%20of%20allowing%20external%20PMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20to%20pass%20that%20man%20or%20woman%20up%20from%20joining%20us%20and%20being%20a%20real%20contributor%20to%20the%20program.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a692577-a430-475e-9933-101cf62135c7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20the%20'indentured%20servitude%20model'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20being%20external%20doesn't%20mean%20there%20are%20different%20risk%20limits%2C%20it%20does%20give%20some%20more%20entrepreneurial%20investors%20the%20chance%20to%20try%20their%20hand%20at%20business%20building.%20And%20though%20the%20firm%20might%20not%20offer%20the%20largest%20compensation%20guarantee%2C%20executives%20believe%20the%20overall%20package%20is%20compelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20our%20competitors%20are%20kind%20of%20an%20indentured%20servitude%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scott%20Nelson%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20client%20partnership%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we've%20tried%20to%20do%2C%20candidly%2C%20is%20be%20people%20that%20those%20portfolio%20managers%20who%20are%20very%20good%2C%20who%20have%20options%2C%20choose%20to%20work%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20the%20firm%20is%20trying%20to%20push%20externally%20is%20that%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bcapital%20partners%2C%20not%20capital%20providers%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStructuring%20risk%20limits%20around%20the%20certain%20type%20of%20strategies%20a%20PM%20runs%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20proof%20they%20don't%20see%20themselves%20as%20a%20one-size-fits-all%2C%20executives%20say%2C%20and%20the%20firm's%20performance%20has%20kept%20pace%20with%20larger%20rivals.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20manager's%20flagship%20strategy%20said%20Crestline%20was%20up%20nearly%2012%25%20in%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2023-hedge-fund-returns-for-citadel-millennium-point72-multistrats-2024-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DKen%2520Griffin%2527s%2520Citadel%2520led%2520the%2CBalyasny%252C%2520Schonfeld%252C%2520and%2520Walleye.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebesting%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20Point72%20and%20Millennium.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20strategy%20is%20up%205.8%25%20through%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20structural%20elements%20to%20how%20we%20engage%20that%20is%2C%20we%20think%2C%20a%20more%20balanced%2C%20fair%20approach%20than%20some%20of%20our%20competitors%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overall%20package%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20punch%20well%20above%20our%20weight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-crestline-summit-expansion-plans-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728482647000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670646f5198738e3a70f45d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22