ncing%20macronutrients%20like%20carbs%20and%20protein%2C%20according%20to%20Roman%20Montijo%2C%20performance%20chef%20and%20registered%20dietitian%20for%20the%20Philadelphia%20Eagles.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%2050%20players%20on%20the%20roster%2C%20Montijo%20said%20he%20works%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnutrition-researcher-eat-to-avoid-afternoon-crash-blood-sugar-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoptimizing%20nutrition%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20performance%20for%20each%20player's%20unique%20needs%2C%20based%20on%20factors%20such%20as%20their%20role%20on%20the%20team%20and%20whether%20it's%20early-season%20training%20or%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20playoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20imagine%20the%20planning%20that%20goes%20into%20making%20sure%20everyone's%20needs%20and%20preferences%20are%20taken%20into%20account.%20We%20might%20switch%20up%20protein%20sources%20%E2%80%94%20chicken%2C%20steak%2C%20seafood%2C%20maybe%20even%20venison%20for%20variety%20%E2%80%94%20but%20modify%20the%20macro%20ratio%20for%20each%20respective%20player's%20plate%2C%26quot%3B%20Montijo%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20coordinated%20by%20MyFitnessPal%2C%20the%20official%20nutrition%20tracking%20app%20of%20the%20Philadelphia%20Eagles%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDifferent%20protein%20sources%20offer%20different%20nutrients%2C%20so%20mixing%20them%20up%20can%20help%20ensure%20you're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-you-eat-same-thing-every-day-and-be-healthy-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%20quinoa%20and%20bone%20broth%2C%20both%20great%20sources%20of%20protein%2C%20are%20team%20favorites%2C%26quot%3B%20Montijo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20potential%20benefits%20of%20adding%20them%20to%20your%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d9272574-2635-4