ssage%20parlour%20to%20treat%20a%20fungal%20infection%20in%20his%20nail.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20boy's%20father%20took%20him%20to%20the%20Luozhendong%20Foot%20Massage%20Parlour%20in%20Chongqing%20Municipality%20of%20China%20to%20treat%20an%20infection%20in%20his%20left%20index%20fingernail%20in%20July.%20The%20shop%20had%20claimed%20that%20it%20had%20a%20medicine%20called%20%26quot%3Bnail%20removing%20cream%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20they%20said%20could%20work%20wonders%20for%20the%20boy's%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20foot%20massage%20parlour%2C%20they%20applied%20the%20boy's%20infected%20fingernail%20and%20bound%20it%20up%20with%20an%20elastic%20bandage.%20The%20father%20paid%20the%20parlour%20600%20yuan%20(%2486%20or%20Rs%20over%207%2C000)%20for%20the%20treatment.%20However%2C%20after%20two%20days%2C%20the%20father%20found%20his%20son's%20finger%20had%20atrophied%20and%20turned%20black%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Farticle%2F3280549%2Fchina-boy-4-has-finger-amputated-after-dad-takes-him-foot-spa-nail-infection%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20then%20rushed%20his%20son%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20where%20doctors%20diagnosed%20gangrene%20-%20a%20serious%20condition%20where%20a%20loss%20of%20blood%20supply%20causes%20body%20tissue%20to%20die.%20The%20doctors%20said%20that%20the%20boy's%20fingertip%20had%20to%20be%20amputated%20to%20avoid%20further%20infections.%20He%20was%20graded%20to%20have%20a%2010th-class%20handicap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20father%20has%20demanded%20more%20than%20200%2C000%20yuan%20(%2429%2C000%20or%20Rs%2023%20lakh)%20in%20compensation%20from%20the%20shop%2C%20which%20rejected%20his%20claim%20thinking%20it%20was%20too%20much.%20The%20father%20also%20reported%20the%20matter%