Edon't%20ever%20post%20pictures%20of%20my%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20your%20privacy%20settings%20are%20locked%20down%2C%20strangers%20might%20not%20see%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20social%20media%20platforms%20still%20see%20(and%20store)%20everything.%20I%20don't%20want%20that%20algorithm%20to%20be%20able%20to%20identify%20my%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20talk%20with%20family%20and%20friends%20about%20this%20policy%2C%20it's%20a%20simple%20conversation.%20If%20I%20see%20someone%20taking%20a%20picture%2C%20I%20ask%20them%20not%20to%20post%20it.%20Sometimes%2C%20that%20opens%20a%20bigger%20conversation%20about%20why%20we%20have%20that%20rule.%20It%20has%20never%20led%20to%20friction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5422b24-d221-42f4-bf10-df0b72a158cf%5C%22%3EI%20rely%20on%20group%20texts%20instead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20group%20texting%20is%20what%20social%20media%20was%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-name-a-group-chat-on-iphone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20group%20text%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20can%20share%20a%20cute%20update%20about%20the%20kids%20or%20send%20a%20picture%20to%20another%20parent%20on%20a%20playdate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20private%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20an%20effective%20way%20of%20building%20connections%20without%20the%20risk%20of%20exposing%20the%20kids'%20faces%20and%20their%20data%20(including%20who%20they%20spend%20time%20with)%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ee298a9-c4db-4b12-8bce-5c2c32e7f1a7%5C%22%3EMy%20tots%20have%200%20screens%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20FaceTime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20two%20younger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-zero-screen-time-toddler-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20have%20zero%20screen%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20don't%20even%20FaceTime%20with%20family.%20I%20think%20it's%20very%20unsettling%20for%20kids%20to%20see%20their%20loved%20ones%20behind%20a%20screen.%20Personally%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20toddlers%20are%20equipped%20to%20understand%20why%20their%20loved%20one%20(who%20they%20normally%20see%20in%20person)%20is%20now%20on%20the%20screen.%20I%20worry%20it%20can%20be%20disorienting%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20benefits%20of%20a%20FaceTime%20chat%20are%20worth%20the%20possible%20emotional%20confusion%20for%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20older%20child%20has%20just%20started%20using%20one%20of%20my%20two%20phones%20to%20text%20me%20when%20I'm%20out.%20That's%20the%20only%20thing%20they're%20allowed%20to%20use%20the%20phone%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20gives%20me%20the%20same%20sense%20of%20security%20that%20I%20used%20to%20have%20with%20a%20landline.%20I%20monitor%20their%20phone%20use%20very%20carefully%20and%20encourage%20other%20parents%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e17f3bf0-a619-4c8e-bdd7-8fc28649a204%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20tech-free%20playdates%20but%20don't%20try%20to%20force%20our%20rules%20on%20others'%20houses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20child%20has%20friends%20over%2C%20we%20have%20a%20no-tech%20rule.%20They%20have%20so%20much%20more%20fun%20outside%20or%20doing%20art%20projects.%20But%20when%20my%20kid%20goes%20to%20a%20friend's%20house%2C%20I%20know%20they%20might%20be%20exposed%20to%20YouTube%20or%20online%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20try%20to%20enforce%20my%20rules%20at%20other%20people's%20houses%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20my%20kid%20might%20get%20more%20sugary%20treats%20at%20a%20friend's%20than%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20my%20eldest%20child%20has%20realized%20they%20have%20more%20fun%20playing%20offline%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20too%20much%20exposure%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222dd02ff2-cbc7-47af-9734-415368e97420%5C%22%3EI%20teach%20my%20kids%20about%20online%20privacy%20and%20critical%20thinking%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20I%20teach%20my%20children%20about%20physical%20privacy%20within%20the%20home%2C%20I%20talk%20with%20them%20about%20online%20privacy%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20touch%20on%20the%20dangers%20of%20being%20online.%20I'll%20say%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20new%20industry%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20filter%20it%20so%20that%20it's%20right%20for%20kids.%26quot%3B%20Or%2C%20%26quot%3BSocial%20media%20can%20lock%20you%20inside%20your%20head%20and%20expose%20you%20to%20ideas%20you're%20not%20ready%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20language%20helps%20kids%20feel%20like%20they're%20being%20protected%2C%20not%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d019108a-1f90-487e-bc6c-801ad4f9234f%5C%22%3EI%20flip%20the%20script%20on%20sharing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20kids%20get%20older%2C%20there's%20more%20opportunity%20for%20friends%20to%20tag%20them%20on%20social%20media%20or%20share%20pictures%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20at%20that%20stage%20yet%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20to%20talk%20with%20my%20children%20so%20they're%20confident%20asking%20friends%20not%20to%20share%20their%20pictures%20if%20that's%20their%20preference.%20I%20want%20to%20create%20allure%20around%20being%20an%20offline%20kid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a3e7f8e-2d05-44eb-a7d0-3f6f6c3f0501%5C%22%3EI%20model%20tech-free%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKids%20do%20what%20their%20parents%20do%2C%20not%20what%20their%20parents%20say.%20That's%20why%20it's%20important%20to%20me%20not%20to%20use%20my%20phone%20or%20technology%20in%20front%20of%20the%20kids.%20When%20they're%20around%2C%20I%20keep%20my%20phone%20up%20high%20and%20well%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20some%20practical%20steps%2C%20we%20can%20navigate%20this%20world%20of%20screens%20to%20keep%20our%20kids%20and%20ourselves%20healthy%20and%20protected%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20everything%20that's%20good%20for%20our%20kids%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20online%20pr