%20the%2090-member%20house.%20Its%20rival%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20sweep%20the%20state%2C%20won%2037%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20results%20would%20have%20been%20different%20had%20the%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20fought%20together%2C%20Mr%20Chadha%20answered%20in%20the%20affirmative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20INDIA%20bloc%20would%20have%20fought%20the%20election%20as%20one%20cohesive%20unit%2C%20the%20results%20could%20have%20been%20diametrically%20opposite%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chadha%2C%20citing%20the%20results%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20fought%20the%20elections%20in%20partnership%20with%20National%20Conference%20and%20it%20won%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20registered%20its%20best%20showing%20in%20the%20state%2C%20wining%2029%20seats%20against%20Congress'%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20INDIA%20bloc%20fought%20as%20an%20alliance%2C%20as%20one%20unit.%20With%20National%20Conference%20and%20Congress%20coming%20together%20and%20the%20BJP%20was%20defeated.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20despite%20best%20efforts%20from%20our%20side%20and%20perhaps%20even%20from%20Congress'%20side%2C%20the%20alliance%20could%20not%20be%20stitched.%20And%20all%20of%20us%20went%20solo%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20outcome%20is%20not%20exactly%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20any%20member%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20even%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chadha%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%20failed%20seat-share%20talks%20between%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushing%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bpragmatic%20approach%26quot%3B%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%2C%20the%20AAP%20leader%20said%20the%20big%20learning%20from%20the%20Haryana%20polls%20has%20been%20that%20%26quot%3Boverconfidence%26quot%3B%20does%20not%20help%20reap%20electoral%20dividends.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http