s%20would%20not%20have%20been%202-3%25.%20but%20far%20more%20and%20far%20greater%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppraising%20the%20Congress'%20performance%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20AAP%20MP%20had%20a%20word%20of%20advice%20for%20the%20grand%20old%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20feel%20that%20there%20are%20now%20separate%20category%20of%20states%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20Congress%20may%20not%20entirely%20on%20its%20own%20be%20able%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%20one-on-one%20fight.%20We%20saw%20that%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(where%20again%20the%20Congress%20was%20expected%20to%20win)%2C%20in%20Rajasthan%20(where%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20maintained%20that%20he%20will%20win)%2C%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20(where%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20also%20appeared%20confident%20of%20winning).%20In%20Haryana%20also%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20something%20similar.%20If%20the%20Congress%20were%20to%20take%20these%20alliance%20partners%20along%2C%20the%20results%20would%20have%20been%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%2C%20however%2C%20exuded%20confidence%20about%20the%20longevity%20and%20importance%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20his%20party's%20continued%20support%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20much%20a%20part%20of%20INDIA%20alliance.%20We%20wish%20to%20remain%20part%20of%20INDIA%20alliance.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20about%20the%20future%20of%20INDIA%20alliance.%20In%202024%2C%20which%20was%20our%20first%20electoral%20outing%20as%20one%20cohesive%20unit%2C%20we%20could%20do%20magic.%20We%20did%20phenomenally%20well%20and%20far%20exceeded%20the%20expectations%20of%20all%20pollsters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B1%20aur%201%20do%20nahi%2C%20gyarah%20ho%20jata%20hai%20when%20all%20of%20us%20come%20together.%20I%20am%20very%20very%20hopeful%20about%20this%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20signin