mir%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20And%20this%20lesson%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20polling%20outcome.%20Despite%20the%20previous%20unstable%20assembly%20(the%20BJP%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20ruling%20PDP-led%20coalition)%2C%20the%20geopolitical%20turmoil%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20the%20controversy%20around%20delimitation%2C%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20chose%20democracy%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EDemocracy%20As%20A%20Lived%20Reality%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20insurgency%20or%20an%20armed%20conflict%20continues%20for%20too%20long%2C%20democracy%20is%20the%20first%20to%20fall.%20Increased%20securitisation%20of%20a%20conflict-ridden%20space%20undermines%20democracy%20not%20just%20as%20a%20political%20philosophy%20concept%20but%20also%20as%20an%20everyday%20lived%20reality.%20Political%20alienation%20is%20often%20the%20beginning%20and%20the%20end%20of%20a%20conflict.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20means%20and%20the%20end%20of%20most%20insurgencies.%20Secessionists%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20therefore%2C%20leaned%20on%20boycotts%20of%20political%20processes%20in%20the%20region.%20These%20boycotts%20were%20successful%20in%20forging%20a%20sense%20of%20identity%2C%20delinked%20from%20New%20Delhi%2C%20in%20a%20section%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir's%20voter%20turnout%20in%202024%20has%20fallen%20marginally%20short%20of%202014.%20Still%2C%20considering%20the%20political%20and%20security%20volatility%20during%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20political%20remapping%20of%20the%20region%2C%20and%20the%20trends%20from%20the%202024%20general%20election%20turnout%2C%20the%20absolute%20figure%20of%2063.88%25%20is%20a%20big%20round%20of%20applause%20for%20Indian%20democracy.%20Not%20only%20were%20the%20calls%20for%20boycotting%20the%20elections%20negligible%2C%20but%20voters%20also%20didn't%20even%20think%20twice%20before%20ignoring%20them.%20The%20pre-poll%20sentiment%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20was%20defined%20by%20buoyancy%20and%20optimism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReigniting%20Faith%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipation%20in%20electoral%20processes%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20indicator%20of%20peace%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20or%20any%20other%20conflict-riddled%20region.%20Democracy%20does%20not%20suit%20all%2C%20and%20efforts%20to%20derail%20it%20are%20the%20strongest%20whenever%20it%20appears%20to%20work%20and%20emerge%20as%20a%20choice.%20For%20peace%2C%20the%20synergy%20of%20formal%20institutions%20is%20a%20prerequisite.%20The%20BJP%20has%20done%20well%20to%20reignite%20people's%20faith%20in%20at%20least%20one%20of%20them%3A%20electoral%20polity.%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20under%20the%20governor's%20rule%20for%20six%20years%2C%20grabbed%20this%20chance%20to%20assert%20itself%20and%20make%20its%20voice%20heard%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20JKNC-Congress%20alliance%20has%20trumped%20religious%20extremism-driven%20parties%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20and%20heavy-handed%20nationalism%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20almost%20a%20decade%20of%20aggressive%20and%20kinetic%20strategy%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20hardliners%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20this%20is%20a%20perfect%20moment%20for%20the%20Indian%20establishment%20to%20rethink%20its%20attitudes%20towards%20conflict%20resolution.%20The%20temptation%20to%20discard%20democracy%20as%20a%20defunct%20system%20is%20at%20its%20highest%20during%20an%20armed%20conflict.%20But%20this%20is%20also%20the%20time%20when%20democracy%20can%20shine%20the%20brightest.%20A%20rights-based%20approach%20to%20conflict%20resolution%20may%20appear%20counter-intuitive%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20only%20lasting%20solution.%20The%20rejection%20of%20the%20right%20to%20vote%20by%20a%20dissatisfied%20bunch%20of%20people%20as%20a%20means%20of%20their%20political%20expression%20can%20be%20the%20first%20sign%20of%20trouble.%20The%20converse%20is%20also%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20Is%20True%20'Normalcy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20may%20not%20feel%20warm%20and%20fuzzy%20about%20the%20assembly%20poll%20results%2C%20but%20New%20Delhi%20has%20all%20the%20reasons%20to%20rejoice.%20This%20is%20what%20'normalcy'%2C%20an%20oft-touted%20catchword%20of%20the%20current%20dispensation%2C%20looks%20and%20feels%20like.%20This%20almost%20violence-free%20election%20is%20the%20festive%20bonus%20that%20everyone%20hoped%20for%2C%20but%20nobody%20could%20have%20been%20sure%20of%20it.%20Reams%20will%20be%20written%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bsuccess%26quot%3B%20of%20this%20election%20within%20the%20security%20paradigm.%20However%2C%20the%20real%20success%20is%20allowing%20the%20decriers%20of%20democracy%20to%20come%20into%20the%20fold.%20After%20long%20periods%20of%20violence%20and%20quasi-violence%20directed%20primarily%20against%20the%20Indian%20state%2C%20this%20election%20is%20an%20affirmation%20of%20the%20core%20principles%20of%20participatory%20democracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20political%20system%2C%20even%20the%20good%20old%20democracy%2C%20can%20and%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20the%20panacea%20for%20all%20ills.%20At%20best%2C%20democracy%20can%20achieve%20an%20environment%20where%20people%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20policies%20feel%20like%20stakeholders.%20This%20precludes%20compulsive%20resistance%20and%20fosters%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership.%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir's%20'problem'%20is%20both%20a%20function%20and%20an%20origin%20of%20political%20alienation%20and%20disempowerment.%20Increased%20participation%20on%20the%20population's%20part%20and%20more%20open-mindedness%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20establishment%20during%20political%20processes%20help%20create%20a%20secure%20environment%20that%20doesn't%20rely%20solely%20on%20securitisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20and%20how%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir's%20political%20arena%20will%20look%20like%20with%20a%20government%20in%20place%20after%20six%20years%20of%20Governor's%20rule%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20For%20now%2C%20these%20lessons%20of%20democracy%20are%20for%20all%20to%20see%20and%20emulate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728481020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fmn8t2sno_jammu-kashmir_625x300_09_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fjammu-kashmir-shows-the-world-democracy-is-not-an-optional-activity-6753056%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20may%20not%20feel%20warm%20and%20fuzzy%20about%20the%20assembly%20poll%20results%2C%20but%20New%20Delhi%20has%20all%20the%20reasons%20to%20rejoice.%20This%20is%20what%20'normalcy'%2C%20an%20oft-touted%20catchword%20of%20the%20current%20dispensation%2C%20looks%20and%20feels%20like.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fjammu-kashmir-shows-the-world-democracy-is-not-an-optional-activity-6753056%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Auschwitz%20survivor%20dies%20aged%20100%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728480780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F10%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-lily-ebert-mbe-obit_6711356.jpg%3F20241009121342%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flily-ebert-auschwitz-survivor-dies-aged-100-13230883%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20last%20remaining%20survivors%20of%20the%20Auschwitz-Birkenau%20concentration%20camp%20has%20died%20aged%20100.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flily-eber