amajwadi%20Party%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20others%20have%20issued%20sharp%20takedowns.%20Even%20the%20normally%20reticent%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20Kashmir%20ally%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20could%20not%20resist%20a%20few%20digs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20were%20focused%20on%20what%20they%20allege%20is%20the%20Congress's%20lack%20of%20respect%20for%20allies%2C%20especially%20the%20smaller%2C%20regional%20ones%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20reach%2C%20more%20than%20size%2C%20is%20crucial%20during%20election.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Barrogance%26quot%3B%20tag%20from%20allies%20have%20hung%20onto%20Congress%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20Now%20more%20than%20the%20Central%20leaders%2C%20it%20is%20the%20state%20leaders%20who%20are%20being%20blamed%20after%20a%20series%20of%20episodes%20when%20smaller%20parties%20had%20been%20rebuffed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECases%20in%20point%20were%20Kamal%20Nath's%20refusal%20to%20allot%20seats%20to%20Samajwadi%20Party%20during%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20elections%20last%20year%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20Congress%20leaders'%20perpetual%20reluctance%20to%20share%20seats%20with%20AAP.%20To%20this%20has%20been%20added%20the%20name%20of%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%2C%20whose%20team%20had%20refused%20to%20share%20space%20with%20AAP%20in%20Haryana.%20In%20each%20case%2C%20the%20state%20leaders%20have%20overridden%20the%20advice%20from%20Central%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20Central%20leadership%20is%20being%20blamed%20for%20allowing%20too%20much%20leeway%20to%20state%20leaders%2C%20who%20at%20every%20instance%20have%20ignored%20messages%20from%20Delhi.%20The%20Congress%20high%20command%20is%20also%20being%20blamed%20for%20failing%20to%20rein%20in%20factionalism%2C%20which%20has%20caused%20hiccups%20in%20states%20including%20Karnataka%20ahead%20of%20government%20formation.%20Or%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Haryana%2C%20crashed%20the%20campaign.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sharpest%20and%20most%20critical%20of%20jabs%20came%20from%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Congress's%20Maharashtra%20ally.%20Its%20timing%20is%20critical%20--%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20western%20state%20and%20amid%20a%20tussle%20over%20seat%20sharing.%20the%20Congress%2C%20after%20its%20hugely%20improved%20performance%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20has%20been%20reluctant%20to%20hand%20over%20six%20seats%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20considered%20its%20stronghold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20editorial%20in%20Sena%20mouthpiece%20Saamna%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20failing%20to%20accommodate%20alliance%20partners%20like%20the%20AAP%20or%20control%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisobedience%20of%20local%20leaders%26quot%3B.%20It%20even%20pointed%20out%20similar%20circumstances%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20last%20year%2C%20indicating%20that%20a%20flexible%20attitude%20could%20have%20changed%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20criticism%20came%20from%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20refused%20to%20allot%20Congress%20more%20than%20two%20seats%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20following%20which%20talks%20for%20state-level%20alliance%20broke%20down%2C%20even%20though%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20remained%20intact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20attitude%20leads%20to%20electoral%20losses%20-%20'if%20we%20feel%20we're%20winning%2C%20we%20will%20not%20accommodate%20a%20regional%20party%20but%2C%20in%20states%20where%20we're%20down%2C%20regional%20parties%20must%20accommodate%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Trinamool's%20Saket%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20needs%20to%20introspect%2C%20focus%20on%20accommodative%20politics...%20Alliance%20principles%20should%20be%20respected...%20Big%20parties%20should%20respect%20regional%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20RJD%20national%20spokesperson%20Professor%20Subodh%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20reluctant%20to%20share%20seats%20with%20Congress%20since%20the%202017%20assembly%20polls%20rout%2C%20has%20thumbs%20downed%20on%20a%20fresh%20request%20for%20by-polls%20to%2010%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20seats%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20chief%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20spoke%20of%20the%20Congress%20being%20doubly%20unhappy%20after%20being%20%26quot%3Btrolled%26quot%3B%20by%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20not%20accepted%20the%20results%20in%20Haryana%2C%20and%20insisted%20on%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Today%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20analysing%20the%20unexpected%20results%20of%20Haryana.%20We%20will%20inform%20the%20Election%20Commission%20about%20the%20complaints%20coming%20from%20many%20assembly%20constituencies%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728478380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Frl97i6ng_haryana-congress_625x300_08_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-turns-on-congress-after-haryana-j-k-results-6752682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%2C%20notwithstanding%20its%20improved%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20is%20back%20to%20square%20one%20after%20its%20dismal%20show%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20--%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20harsh%20criticism%20from%20allies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-turns-on-congress-after-haryana-j-k-results-6752682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'It's%20time%20we%20...'%3A%20Jagan%20Reddy%20backs%20Congress's%20EVM%20'manipulation'%20claim%22%2C%