spa%20centre%20whose%20doors%20were%20locked%20from%20inside.%20She%20asked%20the%20officials%20to%20open%20these%20doors.%20But%20even%20after%20knocking%20several%20times%2C%20no%20one%20opened%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuspicious%20by%20then%2C%20some%20policemen%20entered%20the%20spa%20centre%20through%20the%20roof%20while%20others%20broke%20the%20door%20and%20entered%20inside.%20There%20were%20many%20rooms%20inside%20the%20spa%20centre%2C%20in%20which%20five%20girls%20and%20two%20men%20were%20found%20in%20objectionable%20conditions%2C%20police%20said.%20Sadar%20police%20station%20took%20all%20of%20them%20into%20custody%20on%20suspicion%20of%20prostitution%20and%20all%20of%20them%20are%20being%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20raid%20was%20captured%20on%20camera%20and%20videos%20showed%20several%20women%2C%20trying%20to%20cover%20their%20faces%2C%20and%20men%20inside%20the%20alleged%20spa%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Unethical%20Practices'%20In%20Spa%20Centres%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20spa%20centres%20in%20Barmer%20city%20and%20locals%20have%20been%20complaining%20to%20the%20administration%20about%20many%20of%20these%2C%20alleging%20the%20centres%20are%20involved%20in%20unethical%20practices.%20But%2C%20today's%20raid%20is%20the%20first%20effective%20action%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20people%20in%20the%20know%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20people%20who%20run%20these%20centres%20get%20a%20license%20issued%20from%20the%20Labor%20Department.%20After%20this%2C%20they%20bring%20girls%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Nepal%20and%20run%20a%20prostitution%20business%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20spa%20centres.%20The%20police%20have%20taken%20action%20against%20these%20illegal%20spa%20centres%20several%20times%20but%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20sustained%20action%2C%20these%20people%20get%20back%20to%20these%20practices%20again%20after%20being%20released%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffirst-pics-of-ias-topper-tina-dabis-wedding-to-fellow-officer-are-out-2911779%5C%22%3ETina%20Dabi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20wedding%20to%20fellow%20IAS%20officer%20Pradeep%20Gawande%20made%20headlines%20in%202023%2C%20has%20started%20an%20innovative%20initiative%20-%20%26quot%3BNavo%20Barmer%26quot%3B-%20meaning%20new%20Barmer.%20Under%20the%20initiative%2C%20cleanliness%20campaigns%20are%20being%20run%20in%20the%20city%20using%20new-age%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728475080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ff0htcucg_tina-dabi-raid_625x300_09_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fias-officer-tina-dabi-raids-rajasthan-spa-centre-on-prostitution-suspicion-6752126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20her%20appointment%2C%20Tina%20Dabi%20has%20been%20in%20action%20mode%20-%20she%20is%20sometimes%20seen%20sweeping%20roads%20as%20part%20of%20a%20cleanliness%20campaign%20initiated%20by%20her%20and%20sometimes%20reprimanding%20doctors%20who%20were%20found%20to%20be%20negligent%20during%20hospital%20inspections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infosys%20expands%20partnership%20with%20Microsoft%20to%20boost%20Cloud%2C%20GenAI%20adoption%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728475049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F22%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1724299850-5807.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Finfosys-expands-partnership-with-microsoft-to-boost-cloud-genai-adoption-124100900775_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20will%20infuse%20Microsoft's%20generative%20AI%20suite%20of%20offerings%20across%20its%20Solution%20IP%20portfolio%20