i%20%C2%A0Party%2C%20The%20latter%20has%20declined%20a%20seat-share%20request%20for%20by-polls%20to%2010%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20seats%20later%20this%20year.%20An%20editorial%20in%20Sena%20mouthpiece%20Saamana%20spoke%20of%20the%20Congress's%20ability%20to%20%26quot%3Bturn%20a%20winning%20innings%20into%20a%20defeat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20score%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20earlier%20this%20year%20-%2099%20seats%2C%20up%20from%2052%20in%202019%20--%20had%20earned%20it%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20giving%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20a%20voice%20and%20a%20new%20heft%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20this%20round%20of%20assembly%20polls%20have%20discredited%20exit%20polls%2C%20once%20again.%20The%20Congress%2C%20anticipating%20a%20big%20win%20in%20Haryana%2C%20ended%20up%20second%20with%2037%20seats%20-%20an%20outcome%20that%20has%20been%20attributed%20to%20factionalism%20within%20its%20state%20unit%2C%20complacency%20after%20the%20improved%20performance%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20and%20faulty%20strategy%20that%20placed%20all%20its%20eggs%20in%20the%20Jat%20basket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%2048%20seats%2C%20have%20said%20the%20over-emphasis%20on%20Jats%20has%20only%20polarised%20the%20state%2C%20with%20the%20non-Jat%20voters%20rallying%20behind%20the%20party.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20a%20throwback%20to%20the%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20in%20November%20last%20year.%20The%20Congress%2C%20expected%20to%20retain%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20win%20back%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20was%20left%20empty-handed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20a%20copycat%20situation%20of%20Haryana.%20Said%20to%20be%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20massive%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20government%20of%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20it%20had%20delivered%20a%20massive%20mandate%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20left%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20shaky%20position%20in%20the%20Opposition%20block%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20had%20to%20curb%20its%20ambition%20and%20reinvent%20itself%20as%20a%20team%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20this%20phase%20of%20state%20elections%20can%20affect%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Kashmir%20party%20was%20expected%20be%20the%20dominant%20partner%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20given%20the%20Congress%20performance%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20talk%20on%20whether%20the%20party%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20concern%20that%20the%20outcome%20may%20leave%20the%20party%20in%20a%20weaker%20position%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20where%20talks%20are%20in%20progress%20over%20the%20knotty%20subject%20of%20seat%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Saamna%20editorial%20has%20already%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20failing%20to%20accommodate%20alliance%20partners%20like%20the%20AAP%20or%20control%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisobedience%20of%20local%20leaders%26quot%3B.%20It%20even%20pointed%20out%20similar%20circumstances%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20last%20year%2C%20indicating%20that%20a%20flexible%20attitude%20could%20have%20changed%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20refused%20to%20share%20more%20than%20two%20of%20the%20state's%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20indicated%20they%20have%20been%20vindicated.%20%26quot%3BThis%20attitude%20leads%20to%20electoral%20losses%20-%20'if%20we%20feel%20we're%20winning%2C%20we%20will%20not%20accommodate%20a%20regional%20party%20but%2C%20in%20states%20where%20we're%20down%2C%20regional%20parties%20must%20accommodate%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Trinamool's%20Saket%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728471000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Frg7nflpg_jammu-kashmir-result_625x300_08_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-haryana-j-k-results-can-affect-congress-india-bloc-6751575%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shock%20results%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20in%20Haryana%20--%20an%20election%20it%20was%20expected%20to%20win%20comfortably%20--%20is%20likely%20to%20cast%20its%20shadow%20on%20another%20important%20election%20due%20next%20month%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20might%20put%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%20White%20House%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728471000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F10%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-the-world-podcast_6710860.jpg%3F20241008203348%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-world-podcast-richard-engel-and-yalda-hakim-discuss-how-the-new-us-president-will-handle-war-in-middle-east-13230481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sky%20News%20and%20NBC%20News%20are%20jointly%20launching%20a%20new%20podcast%20on%20global%20affairs%20-%20and%20the%20first%20episode%20is%20out%20now%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20how%20America's%20next%20president%20might%20affect%20the%20crisis%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-world-podcast-richard-engel-and-yalda-hakim-discuss-how-the-new-us-president-will-handle-war-in-middle-east-13230481%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthe-world-podcast-richard-engel-and-yald