hat%20hoping%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370%20from%20the%20people%20who%20snatched%20it%20will%20be%20foolish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%26quot%3BBut%20we%20will%20keep%20this%20issue%20alive.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20talk%20on%20this%20and%20hope%20that%20tomorrow%20there%20will%20be%20a%20change%20of%20government%20in%20the%20country%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20new%20setup%20with%20whom%20we%20can%20discuss%20this%20and%20get%20something%20for%20J-K.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20called%20upon%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20fulfil%20his%20promise%20of%20restoring%20J%26amp%3BK's%20statehood%2C%20stripped%20in%202019%20when%20Article%20370%20was%20abrogated.%20This%20call%20came%20as%20the%20NC-Congress%20alliance%20made%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20a%20key%20election%20plank.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20an%20honourable%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20I%20hope%20he%20lives%20up%20to%20his%20word.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20PM%20Modi's%20promise%20made%20during%20Parliament%20and%20various%20public%20rallies%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20would%20proceed%20without%20unnecessary%20delay.%20He%20rejected%20the%20idea%20that%20statehood%20was%20contingent%20upon%20the%20BJP%20forming%20the%20government%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BNowhere%20has%20the%20BJP%20ever%20said%20-%20first%20there%20will%20be%20our%20government%20and%20then%20statehood.%20The%20PM%20never%20said%20that.%20People%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20spoken%20and%20I%20hope%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20now%20be%20magnanimous%20and%20restore%20statehood%20at%20the%20earliest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20said%20the%20election%20results%20as%20a%20clear%20rejection%20of%20the%202019%20decision%20to%20scrap%20Article%20370.%20The%20NC%20secured%2042%20seats%20in%20the%2090-member%20Assembly%2C%20forming%20a%20majority%20with%20its%20Congress%20ally.%20He%20said%20the%20outcome%20reflected%20the%20people's%20strong%20stance%20against%20the%20BJP's%20policies%2C%20particularly%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20overwhelmingly%20voted%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20won%20both%20the%20Budgam%20and%20Ganderbal%20seats%2C%20a%20big%20recovery%20after%20his%20setback%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20As%20J%26amp%3BK%20prepares%20for%20a%20new%20government%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%20working%20relationship%26quot%3B%20with%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%2C%20however%2C%20red-flagged%20the%20strained%20relationship%20between%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20current%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20Manoj%20Sinha%2C%20urging%20the%20LG%20to%20foster%20better%20ties%20with%20the%20incoming%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728469020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F7mg23qro_omar-abdullah_625x300_09_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-kashmir-elections-seeking-article-370-restoration-from-bjp-foolish-omar-abdullah-6751418%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22National%20Conference%20(NC)%20Vice%20President%20Omar%20Abdullah%20has%20said%20that%20seeking%20the%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20very%20party%20responsible%20for%20its%20removal%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20%26quot%3Bfoolish.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turkey%20moves%20to%20evacuate%20nationals%20from%20Lebanon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728468224000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114078412%2Cimgsize-1537403.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fturkey-moves