%3Cem%3E(Above%20images%20of%20Kailash%20Sankhala%2C%20J%20Vijaya%20%26amp%3B%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%3A%20What%20it%20means%20to%20co-exist%20with%20snow%20leopards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20a%20famous%20father%20in%20Colonel%20Chewang%20Rinchen%2C%20a%20decorated%20Ladakhi%20soldier%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246169%2Fladakh-snow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-saviours-rinchen-wangchuk-tsewang-namgail-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERinchen%20Wangchuk%3C%2Fa%3E%20forged%20his%20own%20path.%20As%20a%20wildlife%20researcher%20from%20Ladakh%2C%20he%20framed%20a%20question%20that%20would%20address%20the%20fundamental%20challenge%20of%20snow%20leopard%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20reconcile%20the%20notion%20of%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20local%20communities%20who%20lose%20their%20livestock%2C%20particularly%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20to%20these%20elusive%20creatures%3F%20To%20answer%20this%20question%2C%20he%20established%20the%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy-India%20Trust%20(SLC-IT)%20in%202000%20to%20promote%20local%20efforts%20towards%20community-based%20conservation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20taking%20a%20variety%20of%20steps%20to%20help%20local%20farmers%20and%20nomads%20protect%20their%20livestock%20from%20snow%20leopards%2C%20thus%20preventing%20man-animal%20conflicts%2C%20he%20also%20pioneered%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20models%20of%20eco-tourism%20with%20conservation-linked%20homestays%20located%20in%20critical%20snow%20leopard%20habitats%20and%20along%20popular%20trekking%20routes.%20These%20successful%20models%20of%20community-based%20tourism%20in%20the%20Hemis%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20Sham%20region%2C%20and%20Zanskar%20still%20stand%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe