mbazar-palace-in-india-5-1726573670-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-5-1726573670-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366184%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20gives%20guests%20a%20peek%20into%20the%20colonial%20history%20of%20Murshidabad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20was%20just%2013%20years%20old%20when%20she%20got%20married%20and%20I%20was%20born%20a%20year%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20gets%20his%20resilience%20and%20optimism%20from%20her.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20had%20to%20forgo%20her%20education%20when%20I%20was%20born.%20But%20when%20I%20started%20school%2C%20she%20resumed%20studying.%20She%20graduated%2C%20got%20a%20national%20scholarship%20and%20qualified%20in%20hotel%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20her%20new-found%20knowledge%20and%20culinary%20prowess%2C%20Supriya%20started%20a%20bakery%20in%20her%20house%20that%20in%20coming%20years%20would%20become%20a%20brand%2C%20%E2%80%98Sugar%20and%20Spice%E2%80%99.%20A%20common%20household%20name%20in%20the%20region%20today%2C%20%E2%80%98Sugar%20and%20Spice%E2%80%99%20has%20three%20factories%2C%20one%20each%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Kasim%20Bazar%20and%20Siliguri.%20While%20the%20confectionery%20brand%20was%20one%20of%20the%20successful%20projects%20the%20family%20lays%20claim%20to%2C%20the%20other%20remains%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20grand%20%3Cem%3ERajbari%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERediscovering%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%3A%20From%20obscurity%20to%20opulence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupriya%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20determination%20got%20the%20family%20brainstorming%20about%20ways%20in%20which%20they%20could%20revive%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20ancestral%20palace.%20But%2060%20years%20of%20neglect%20meant%20that%20the%20palace%20had%20been%20made%20void%20of%20most%20of%20its%20treasures.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20furniture%2C%20aside%20from%20that%20in%20the%20main%20drawing%20room%2C%20had%20vanished.%20We%20are%20lucky%20to%20have%20some%20of%20the%20mirrors%2C%20sideboard%20tables%20and%20sofas%2C%20and%20have%20restored%20those.%20But%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290529%2Fancient-photography-techniques-in-india-madhavan-pillai-research-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20generations%20of%20photos%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20lost%20when%20the%20house%20was%20cleaned%20by%20the%20Government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20when%20they%20resolved%20to%20rebuild%20the%20ancestral%20property%20as%20a%20heritage%20hotel%2C%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20retrieve%20these%20artefacts.%20Today%2C%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%2C%20boasting%2014%20rooms%2C%20which%20can%20accommodate%2040%20guests%20at%20a%20time%2C%20is%20a%20heritage%20hotel%20recognised%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Tourism%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20bear%20in%20mind%2C%20this%20recognition%20has%20come%20after%20decades%20of%20effort.%20Years%20ago%2C%20as%20the%20Roys%20vetted%20the%20situation%20that%20lay%20before%20them%20%E2%80%93%20a%20castle%20in%20ruins%20%E2%80%93%20they%20were%20perplexed%20about%20where%20to%20start.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20castle%20was%20a%20mediaeval%20one%20and%20so%20torches%20were%20popular.%20After%20the%20cleaning%20process%20was%20complete%2C%20we%20began%20work%20on%20the%20electricity%20and%20the%20wiring%2C%20the%20water%20connections%2C%20sinks%20and%20toilets.%20We%20had%20to%20replace%20broken%20furniture.%20And%20I%20think%20we%20changed%20almost%20500%20beams%20inside%20the%20palace%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C