20the%20main%20building%2C%20the%20north%20corridor%2C%20the%20ballroom%20annexes%2C%20dining%20room%20artefacts%2C%20Andar%20Mahal%20(an%20indoor%20space%20where%20the%20women%20of%20the%20palace%20lived)%2C%20some%20of%20the%20temples%20and%20the%20interior%20gardens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20that%20it%20has%20been%20chronicled%20by%20books%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98A%20History%20of%20Murshidabad%E2%80%99%20by%20Major%20Walsh%20(1902)%20and%20%E2%80%98The%20Musnud%20of%20Murshidabad%E2%80%99%20(1905).%20They%20detail%20the%20fanfare%20and%20allure%20that%20Kasim%20Bazar%20enjoyed%20prior%20to%20the%20Battle%20of%20Plassey%20(1757)%20when%20the%20city%20was%20a%20major%20trading%20centre%20and%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20exporting%20hubs%20in%20the%20Eastern%20part%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20us%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20royal%20lineage%2C%20Pallab%20points%20to%20how%20the%20erstwhile%20British%20rulers%20used%20to%20create%20royalty%20by%20giving%20titles.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20were%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emaharaja%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Our%20family%20was%20recognised%20for%20our%20charitable%20work%20and%20three%20successive%20generations%20received%20the%20title%20of%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20this%20was%20an%20individual%20title%20it%20faded%20with%20the%20death%20of%20the%20person.%20This%20is%20why%2C%20Pallab%20explains%2C%20he%20and%20his%20father%20do%20not%20carry%20the%20title%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPut%20your%20royal%20robes%20on!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20was%20the%20last%20time%20you%20were%20made%20to%20feel%20like%20royalty%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%2C%20mornings%20are%20both%20exciting%20and%20restful.%20Sip%20on%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20(or%20many%20of%20them)%20as%20you%20relish%20your%20spread%20of%20breakfast.%20The%20stillness%20is%20broken%20only%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20birds.%20Whether%20it%20is%20a%20session%20of%20tennis%20on%20the%20court%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350504%2Fmarble-palace-kolkata-museum-tour-first-private-zoo-raja-rajendra-mullick-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalk%20around%20the%20palace%20gardens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20sitting%20by%20the%20ponds%20and%20listening%20to%20the%20music%20that%20drifts%20from%20one%20of%20the%20live%20band%20shows%20put%20up%20for%20the%20guests%2C%20serenity%20is%20in%20the%20details.%20Naturally%2C%20the%20guests%20who%20come%20to%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20from%20around%20the%20world%20find%20themselves%20wishing%20they%20could%20take%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20place%20back%20with%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20royal%20residence%20reflects%20Bengali%20style%20interspersed%20with%20colonial%20architecture%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366188%5C%22%20heig